name: The_Summoning (I)
description:
HD1080p, colour/silent, 00'10", loop, Alexandra Crouwers, 2020

An hommage to the Star Trek's teleportation ghosts as seen in the original series. The location is a park on the volcanic island of Tenerife (March 2018). 

A low-res .gif of The_Summoning (I) is used as a header for this April 14, 2021 blog-post: https://www.theappealoftheunreal.com/research-areas/the-unreal-first-notes-on-non-fungible-tokens/
